<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<body style="font-family: sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h2>Your PRO Plan Expires Soon</h2>
  <p>Hi {{ ownerFirstName }},</p>
  <p>Your <strong>BarberPro PRO</strong> plan will expire on <strong>{{ endDate }}</strong>.</p>
  <p>Renew now for 299,000 ₫ to avoid any interruption to your service.</p>
  <p style="margin: 24px 0;">
    <a href="{{ renewUrl }}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 32px; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;">
      Renew Now
    </a>
  </p>
  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">If you don't renew, you will lose access to PRO features after the expiration date.</p>
  <p style="margin-top: 24px;">{{ shopName }}</p>
</body>
</html>
